{
  "stem": "543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we have to get them for-- by a doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now the-- the-- the Russians started to-- to pester us also in the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came in with the-- with the guns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one wanted to sleep with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the boy, they said they-- they couldn't Anyway, they said, it was-- it's much better when you go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, so-- not better because they took us-- they took us-- found-- they find a little rowboat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took us over the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one side were the Russians at the Elbe, and the other the side of Elbe were the-- the Americans and the English people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they rowed us over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to go back where there was more people that they have to look after.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there we were on an-- on an-- on-- on an-- a-- on-- on-- on the end of the water.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lillian couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had to find help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was looking around for soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, first I saw one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't understand we walked",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, I remembered my number on my arm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was in about in April/May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had put my arm-- my arm up and I said, here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said-- and then he-- and he was talking to the-- called right away people go, over here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have somebody from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he asked me where I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said I was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, and before I knew it, they picked me up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they took me to the caserne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where the soldiers were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The caserne is a Dutch word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like-- like an-- how you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where-- where the soldiers are?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
